1.0.name: wordpress/google-analytics-export
1.0.description:
Google Analytics can provide statistics on visitors. No data in the database does not keep the Wordpress plugin. Page every time you boot the last 30 days and the graphics and text as taking your Analytics data transmissions. You can also view stats Blog.
